snippet.title: FINAL FANTASY XIV Patch 7.1 - Crossroads
snippet.description:
Enjoy a preview of FINAL FANTASY XIV Patch 7.1, Crossroads─the first major update following the release of #Dawntrail!

#FFXIV Patch 7.1 launches on 12 November 2024!
Learn more: https://sqex.to/y8Tbf
